title: Bullish Two Hundred Day Moving Average Cross - KEM - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of KEMET Corp. (Symbol: KEM) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $18.26, changing hands as high as $18.50 per share. KEMET Corp. shares are currently trading up about 5.4% on the day.
